'''1986年世界斯诺克锦标赛'''又称'''1986年使馆世界斯诺克锦标赛'''，是1986年4月19日至5月5日在英格兰[[谢菲尔德|谢菲尔德]][[克鲁西布剧院|克鲁西布剧院]]举办的职业[[斯诺克|斯诺克]][[斯诺克职业选手世界排名|排名赛]]。比赛由[[世界职业台球与斯诺克协会|世界职业台球与斯诺克协会]]主办，是克鲁西布剧院[[1977年世界斯诺克锦标赛|1977年]]开始连续举办的第十届[[世界斯诺克锦标赛|世界斯诺克锦标赛]]，也是1985至1986年斯诺克赛季第六场和最后一场排名赛。大赛由[[使馆_(香烟)|使馆]]香烟公司赞助，奖金总额35万英镑，冠军奖金七万英镑。

卫冕冠军[[丹尼斯·泰勒|丹尼斯·泰勒]]在[[1985年世界斯诺克锦标赛决赛|上一年决赛]]以18比17打败[[史蒂夫·戴维斯|史蒂夫·戴维斯]]首次拿到世锦赛冠军，结果本届赛事第一轮就以六比十被[[迈克·哈雷特|迈克·哈雷特]]淘汰。世界排名第16的[[乔·约翰逊_(斯诺克球手)|乔·约翰逊]]在决赛以18比12战胜戴维斯，拿到职业生涯唯一的世锦赛冠军。赛前庄家对约翰逊获胜的赔率达1赔150。本届赛事共有20次单杆破百分，并以戴维斯在八强赛第一局打出的134分最高。

== 概述 ==
[[世界斯诺克锦标赛|世界斯诺克锦标赛]]是[[世界职业台球与斯诺克协会|世界职业台球与斯诺克协会]]主办的年度职业[[斯诺克|斯诺克]]赛事<ref name="Harris2020">{{cite book | editor-first1 = John | editor-last1 = Nauright | editor-first2 = Sarah | editor-last2 = Zipp | title = Routledge Handbook of Global Sport | first = Luke J. | last = Harris | chapter = 21. Snooker and billiards | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=htTHDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT277&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | date = 2020-01-03 | publisher = Taylor & Francis | location = Abingdon | isbn = 978-1-138-88723-7 | pages = 227–237 | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220525/https://books.google.com/books?id=htTHDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT277}}</ref>。斯诺克源自19世纪驻印英国军人<ref name="Williams2015">{{cite book | first = Victoria R. | last = Williams | title = Weird Sports and Wacky Games around the World: From Buzkashi to Zorbing | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | date = 2015-04-28 | publisher = ABC-CLIO | location = Santa Barbara | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=lpDdBwAAQBAJ&pg=PA286&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220523/https://books.google.com/books?id=lpDdBwAAQBAJ&pg=PA286 | isbn = 978-1-61069-639-5 | page = 286 | dead-url = no}}</ref>，在[[不列颠群岛|不列颠群岛]]非常流行<ref name="Harris2020" />。进入现代后，世锦赛从1969年开始改为淘汰赛制<ref>{{cite news | title = John Higgins eyes more crucible titles | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/othersports/snooker/5276218/John-Higgins-eyes-more-Crucible-titles.html | newspaper = The Telegraph | location = London | date = 2009-05-05 | access-date = 2021-03-10 | dead-url = no | quote = the modern era, which began in 1969 when the World Championship became a knockout event. | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201009141133/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/othersports/snooker/5276218/John-Higgins-eyes-more-Crucible-titles.html | archive-date = 2020-10-09 }}</ref>，逐渐风靡世界，在中国大陆、香港、泰国等东亚和东南亚国家及地区特别受欢迎<ref name="Mf3Af">{{cite web | title = The Rise Of China | work = World Snooker | date = 2018-02-26 | access-date = 2021-02-20 | url = https://wst.tv/the-rise-of-china/ | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210125042234/https://wst.tv/the-rise-of-china/ | archive-date = 2021-01-25 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Wilson | first = Bill | date = 2015-04-24 | title = Snooker looks to cue up more big breaks in China | url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-32429022 | work = BBC News | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210116184829/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-32429022 | archive-date = 2021-01-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Chinese snooker world watches idol Ding with high hopes |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-snooker-world-ding-idUSKBN17V0CZ |accessdate=2021-10-22 |work=Reuters |date=2017-04-29 |language=en |archive-date=2021-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211026022647/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-snooker-world-ding-idUSKBN17V0CZ }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=More China kids to play snooker - Ding |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/snooker/50718400 |accessdate=2021-10-22 |work=BBC Sport |archive-date=2021-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211025201655/https://www.bbc.com/sport/snooker/50718400 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Hale |first1=Thomas |last2=Yang |first2=Yuan |title=China ready for shot at snooker glory as it pushes to dominate sport |url=https://www.ft.com/content/973ccf14-ad5a-4b0e-b6f6-9fad8634f3b0 |accessdate=2021-10-22 |work=Financial Times |date=2021-04-16 |archive-date=2022-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220424044405/https://www.ft.com/content/973ccf14-ad5a-4b0e-b6f6-9fad8634f3b0 }}</ref>。

首届世锦赛于[[1927年世界斯诺克锦标赛|1927年]]举办，[[乔·戴维斯|乔·戴维斯]]在英格兰[[伯明翰|伯明翰]][[比尔·坎金|坎金大厅]]的决赛胜出<ref name="Everton2012">{{cite book | first = Clive | last = Everton | title = Black Farce and Cue Ball Wizards: The Inside Story of the Snooker World | year = 2012 | publisher = Mainstream Publishing | location = Edinburgh | isbn = 978-1-78057-568-1 | page = 23}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = History of Snooker – a Timeline | url = https://wpbsa.com/about-us/history/ | publisher = World Professional Billiards and Snooker Association | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2021-01-07 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210107025119/https://wpbsa.com/about-us/history/}}</ref>。[[谢菲尔德|谢菲尔德]][[克鲁西布剧院|克鲁西布剧院]]从1977年开始举办斯诺克世锦赛<ref name="Clarke2008">{{cite book | first = Gary | last = Clarke | title = A Billiards and Snooker Compendium | location = Rothersthorpe | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | dead-url = no | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=-1gXfvMbyJAC&pg=PA36&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | year = 2008 | publisher = Paragon Publishing | isbn = 978-1-899820-46-7 | page = 36 | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220524/https://books.google.com/books?id=-1gXfvMbyJAC&pg=PA36}}</ref>。1986年世锦赛同样由[[世界职业台球与斯诺克协会|世界职业台球与斯诺克协会]]主办，32名职业选手按[[单败淘汰制|单败淘汰制]]一对一竞争，每轮比赛至少有十余局定胜负。参赛选手除正式比赛前的资格赛选拔外，还邀请[[斯诺克职业选手世界排名|世界斯诺克排名]]位居前列的选手。<ref name="2019 Betfred WSC">{{cite web | title = 2019 Betfred World Snooker Championship | website = wst.tv | publisher = World Professional Billiards and Snooker Association | access-date = 2021-03-10 | url = https://wst.tv/tickets/2019-betfred-world-snooker-championship/ | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210111111430/https://wst.tv/tickets/2019-betfred-world-snooker-championship/ | archive-date = 2021-01-11}}</ref><ref name="Crucible Draw And Format">{{cite web | title = Crucible Draw And Format | website = wst.tv | publisher = World Professional Billiards and Snooker Association | date = 2018-04-09 | access-date = 2021-03-10 | url = https://wst.tv/crucible-draw-format/ | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210108211336/https://wst.tv/crucible-draw-format/ | archive-date = 2021-01-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref>世界排名前16的球员作为种子选手自动晋级正式赛，剩下16个名额从资格赛选拔<ref name="2019 Betfred WSC" /><ref name="Crucible Draw And Format" />。

