== 赛程概况 ==
=== 资格赛 ===
1986年3月26日至4月6日，资格赛在[[普雷斯顿公会堂|普雷斯顿公会堂]]举行<ref name="CWFEB86">{{cite magazine | date = 1986-02 | title = When and where | magazine = Cueworld | publisher = Snooker Publications | pages = 19}}</ref>，均采用19局10胜制<ref name="CWMAY86" />。[[乔·奥博伊|乔·奥博伊]]（{{lang|en|Joe O'Boye}}）以八比十不敌[[比尔·奥利弗|比尔·奥利弗]]（{{lang|en|Bill Oliver}}），但打出的118分是赛上第一个单杆破百分。[[保罗·桑利|保罗·桑利]]（{{lang|en|Paul Thornley}}）以十比三战胜德里克·米尼（{{lang|en|Derek Mienie}}）并打出单杆126分。[[约翰·哈格里夫斯|约翰·哈格里夫斯]]（{{lang|en|John Hargreaves}}）以二比九落后[[伯尼·米克森|伯尼·米克森]]（{{lang|en|Bernie Mikkelsen}}）时连追五局到七比九，但还是在第17局失利后淘汰。[[戴夫·吉尔伯特|戴夫·吉尔伯特]]（{{lang|en|Dave Gilbert}}）在五比七落后时同样连赢五局，反以十比七压倒[[罗杰·巴尔斯|罗杰·巴尔斯]]（{{lang|en|Roger Bales}}）。老牌职业球手[[伯纳德·贝内特|伯纳德·贝内特]]（{{lang|en|Bernard Bennett}}）首轮遭[[萨克查·西姆·恩加姆|萨克查·西姆·恩加姆]]（{{lang|en|Sakchai Sim Ngam}}）[[橫掃|橫掃]]，[[詹姆士·吉安纳罗斯|詹姆士·吉安纳罗斯]]（{{lang|en|James Giannaros}}）、[[吉姆·伦佩|吉姆·伦佩]]（{{lang|en|Jim Rempe}}）和韦恩·桑德森（{{lang|en|Wayne Sanderson}}）自行退赛。<ref name="CWMAY86" />

进入第二轮后，[[1986年苏格兰职业斯诺克锦标赛|苏格兰职业锦标赛]]冠军[[史蒂芬·亨得利|史蒂芬·亨得利]]打出单杆141分并战胜[[帕迪·布朗|帕迪·布朗]]（{{lang|en|Paddy Browne}}），为他赢得1750美元的资格赛单杆最高分奖金。比赛竞争激烈，布朗一度从三比八追到八比九，但亨得利最后以十比九获胜。<ref name="CWMAY86" />与[[鲍勃·查珀隆|鲍勃·查珀隆]]（{{lang|en|Bob Chaperon}}）打成八平后，[[弗兰克·乔尼克|弗兰克·乔尼克]]（{{lang|en|Frank Jonik}}）在下一局落后22分时认输，但此时台面上从棕球到黑球一共就有22分，完全有望追平或是做斯诺克反超。第18局他又在落后53分时认输，此时台面还有六个红球，即便不做斯诺克，理论最高分也有75分，这次放弃导致乔尼克以八比十淘汰。<ref name="CWMAY86" />[[吉米·范·雷斯伯格|吉米·范·雷斯伯格]]（{{lang|en|Jimmy van Rensberg}}）在决胜局靠最后的黑球以42比41战胜[[伊恩·威廉姆森|伊恩·威廉姆森]]（{{lang|en|Ian Williamson}}）。[[史蒂夫·纽伯里|史蒂夫·纽伯里]]（{{lang|en|Steve Newbury}}）在比赛路上遇到[[車禍|車禍]]，汽车损毁、夫人受伤，但他还是以十比五淘汰[[奥普拉科什·阿格拉瓦尔|奥普拉科什·阿格拉瓦尔]]（{{lang|en|Omprakesh Agrawal}}）。第二轮也出现一次横扫，[[雷·埃德蒙兹|雷·埃德蒙兹]]（{{lang|en|Ray Edmonds}}）以十比零打败[[比利·凯利|比利·凯利]]（{{lang|en|Billy Kelly}}）。<ref name="CWMAY86" />

亨得利第三轮打出单杆117分和91分，以十比八战胜[[韦恩·琼斯|韦恩·琼斯]]（{{lang|en|Wayne Jones}}），琼斯一度从三比七追成八平，但亨得利笑到最后<ref>{{Cite news | issn = 0140-0460 | title = Sport in Brief: Pals' act | newspaper = [[泰晤士报|The Times]] | location = London | date = 1986-04-04 | page = 32 | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F90AC83C1721336 | access-date = 2020-05-08 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220547/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F0F90AC83C1721336 }}{{Subscription required}}</ref>。[[莱斯·多德|莱斯·多德]]（{{lang|en|Les Dodd}}） 对阵前世锦赛推广人[[迈克·沃特森|迈克·沃特森]]（{{lang|en|Mike Watterson}}）时只输一局，[[彼得·弗朗西斯科|彼得·弗朗西斯科]]（{{lang|en|Peter Francisco}}）也以十比一击败前[[撞球|台球]]和斯诺克世界冠军[[佛雷德·戴維斯|佛雷德·戴維斯]]<ref name="CWMAY86" /><ref>{{cite news | date = 1998-04-16 | title = Tributes to cue king Fred Davis | archive-date = 2021-01-12 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/sport/79178.stm | work = BBC News | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210112090526/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/sport/79178.stm | dead-url = no}}</ref>。一个月前刚拿下1986年[[世界撞球錦標賽_(英式撞球)|世界台球锦标赛]]冠军的[[罗比·福尔德瓦里|罗比·福尔德瓦里]]（{{lang|en|Robby Foldvari}}）以十比七淘汰[[1974年世界斯诺克锦标赛|1974年世界斯诺克锦标赛]]亚军[[格雷厄姆·迈尔斯|格雷厄姆·迈尔斯]]（{{lang|en|Graham Miles}}）<ref>{{cite book | last = Everton | first = Clive | year = 2012 | title = A History of Billiards | publisher = englishbilliards.org | location = Malmesbury, Wiltshire | isbn = 978-0-9564054-5-6 | page = 174}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Everton | first = Clive | date = 2014-10-15 | title = Graham Miles: Former World Snooker finalist dies aged 73 | url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/snooker/29629237 | work = BBC Sport | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905100812/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/snooker/29629237 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。前世界冠军[[約翰·史賓塞_(英國運動員)|约翰·斯宾塞]]以十比七战胜纽伯里取得正式赛资格，他在正式赛的对手[[亞歷克斯·希金斯|亞歷克斯·希金斯]]也曾获世界冠军<ref name="CWMAY86" />。亨得利以六比三领先后再以十比九打败[[丹尼·奥凯恩|丹尼·奥凯恩]]（{{lang|en|Dene O'Kane}}），刷新克鲁西布剧院世锦赛历史上最年轻的资格赛晋级选手纪录。第四轮共有三名世界排行前32的[[种子_(体育运动)|种子选手]]淘汰，除奥凯恩外，另外两人分别是[[马克·怀尔德曼|马克·怀尔德曼]]（{{lang|en|Mark Wildman}}）和[[默多·麦克劳德|默多·麦克劳德]]（{{lang|en|Murdo MacLeod}}），怀尔德曼是在九比六领先埃德蒙兹并拿到赛点时被对手连追四局，麦克劳德以六比十不敌[[丹尼·福勒|丹尼·福勒]]（{{lang|en|Danny Fowler}}）。<ref name="CWMAY86" />

=== 第一轮 ===
[[File:Dennis_Taylor,_2004.jpg|thumb]]第一轮淘汰]]
正式赛第一轮于4月19至24日举行，采用19局10胜制，分两阶段<ref name="Global Snooker" /><ref>{{Cite news | issn = 0140-0460 | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = Snooker: White's world chance | newspaper = The Times | location = London | page = 40 | date = 1986-04-19 | access-date = 2020-05-09 | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F90ACEFEFCACC81 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220526/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F0F90ACEFEFCACC81 }}{{Subscription required}}</ref>。卫冕冠军[[丹尼斯·泰勒|丹尼斯·泰勒]]首轮遇到[[迈克·哈雷特|迈克·哈雷特]]（{{lang|en|Mike Hallett}}）后连输七局，首阶段结束时以一比八落后，据[[克里夫·艾佛頓|克里夫·艾佛頓]]报道，泰勒比赛时看起来有些心不在焉<ref>{{Cite news | last = Everton | first = Clive | title = Snooker: Torture for a jaded Taylor | newspaper = The Sunday Times | location = London | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F925855E2A20A42 | date = 1986-04-20 | access-date = 2020-05-08 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220545/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F0F925855E2A20A42 }}{{Subscription required}}</ref>。接下来泰勒连追五局，但还是以六比十淘汰。[[1978年世界斯诺克锦标赛|1978年]]的约翰·斯宾塞<ref>{{Cite news | title = 1978: Reardon makes it six | work = BBC Sport | date = 2003-04-18 | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2004-05-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210107024927/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/snooker/2953755.stm | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/snooker/2953755.stm | dead-url = no}}</ref>、[[1980年世界斯诺克锦标赛|1980年]]的[[泰瑞·格里菲斯|泰瑞·格里菲斯]]<ref>{{Cite news | title = 1980: Thorburn outguns Higgins | work = BBC Sport | date = 2003-04-18 | access-date = 2021-03-10 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/snooker/2953789.stm | archive-date = 2021-03-10 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210107024938/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/snooker/2953789.stm}}</ref>、[[1981年世界斯诺克锦标赛|1981年]]的[[克里夫·索本|克里夫·索本]]<ref>{{Cite news | title = 1981: Davis begins his reign | work = BBC Sport | date = 2003-04-18 | access-date = 2021-03-10 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-01-07 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/snooker/2953801.stm | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210107024925/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/snooker/2953801.stm}}</ref>，还有[[1982年世界斯诺克锦标赛|1982年]]的[[史蒂夫·戴维斯|史蒂夫·戴维斯]]<ref>{{Cite news | title = 1982: Higgins' emotional win | work = BBC Sport | date = 2003-04-18 | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2021-01-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210117223651/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/snooker/2953889.stm | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/snooker/2953889.stm | dead-url = no}}</ref>都在克鲁西布剧院卫冕失败，这种首获世锦赛冠军者无法卫冕的情况人称“[[克鲁西布诅咒|克鲁西布诅咒]]”<ref name="BBC 1986">{{cite news | title = 1986: Johnson stuns snooker world | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/snooker/2953941.stm | work = BBC Sport | date = 2003-04-18 | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210107024927/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/snooker/2953941.stm | archive-date = 2021-01-07 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Baxter | first = Trevor | title = Dott falls to the 'Crucible curse' | archive-date = 2020-09-03 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/othersports/snooker/2311594/Dott-falls-to-the-Crucible-curse.html | newspaper = The Telegraph | location = London | date = 2007-04-22 | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200903211706/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/othersports/snooker/2311594/Dott-falls-to-the-Crucible-curse.html}}</ref>。二号种子史蒂夫·戴维斯以十比四打败埃德蒙兹<ref name="TIMES21A">{{Cite news | issn = 0140-0460 | title = Snooker: No rub of green | newspaper = The Times | location = London | date = 1986-04-21 | page = 40 | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F90ACFBB5FF1A00 | access-date = 2020-05-08 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220551/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F0F90ACFBB5FF1A00 }}{{Subscription required}}</ref>，三号种子索本以十比五战胜[[比尔·温本纽克|比尔·温本纽克]]（{{lang|en|Bill Werbeniuk}}），四号种子[[托尼·诺尔斯|托尼·诺尔斯]]（{{lang|en|Tony Knowles}}）以十比九险胜[[尼尔·富尔兹|尼尔·富尔兹]]（{{lang|en|Neal Foulds}}）<ref name="FRISKIN25A">{{Cite news | issn = 0140-0460 | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = Snooker: Knowles recovers to defeat Foulds | newspaper = The Times | location = London | page = 32 | date = 1986-04-25 | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F90AD2D9E953FC7 | access-date = 2020-05-09 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220548/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F0F90AD2D9E953FC7 }}{{Subscription required}}</ref>。

16号种子[[乔·约翰逊_(斯诺克球手)|乔·约翰逊]]以十比三淘汰[[戴夫·马丁|戴夫·马丁]]（{{lang|en|Dave Martin}}），这是他第三次参加世锦赛，也是首次在正式赛取胜<ref name="TIMES21A" />。[[吉米·怀特|吉米·怀特]]以十比七战胜[[约翰·维尔戈|约翰·维尔戈]]（{{lang|en|John Virgo}}），而且最后一局打出单杆121分<ref name="FRISKIN22A">{{Cite news | issn = 0140-0460 | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = Snooker: White's brilliant finish | newspaper = The Times | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F90AD02067C67E6 | access-date = 2020-05-08 | location = London | date = 1986-04-22 | page = 29 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220615/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F0F90AD02067C67E6 }}{{Subscription required}}</ref>。三获世锦赛冠军的斯宾塞以七比十不敌希金斯，这是他最后一次参加世锦赛<ref>{{cite web | title = John Spencer player profile | url = https://www.snookerdatabase.co.uk/PlayerDetails.aspx?PlayerKey=56&tourns=WC&plStat=2 | website = Snooker Database | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2016-03-07 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307173047/http://www.snookerdatabase.co.uk/PlayerDetails.aspx?PlayerKey=56&tourns=WC&plStat=2}}</ref>。未来七获世锦赛冠军的亨得利在克鲁西布剧院首秀对阵[[威利·索恩|威利·索恩]]（{{lang|en|Willie Thorne}}）时以八比十失利<ref name="BBC 1986" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Stephen Hendry player profile | url = https://www.snookerdatabase.co.uk/PlayerDetails.aspx?PlayerKey=2&tourns=WC&plStat=2 | website = Snooker Database | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2018-08-07 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180807190250/http://www.snookerdatabase.co.uk/PlayerDetails.aspx?PlayerKey=2&tourns=WC&plStat=2}}</ref><ref name="FRISKIN23A">{{Cite news | issn = 0140-0460 | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = Snooker: Teenager pushes Thorne to brink | newspaper = The Times | location = London | date = 1986-04-23 | page = 38 | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F90AD03C3E5C825 | access-date = 2020-05-08 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220555/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F0F90AD03C3E5C825 }}{{Subscription required}}</ref>。亨得利此时只有17岁3个月大，创下世锦赛史上最年轻选手纪录<ref>{{cite news | title = World Snooker: Stephen Hendry wins Crucible qualifier | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/snooker/17714402 | date = 2012-04-15 | work = BBC Sport | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112022837/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/snooker/17714402 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。福勒也是首次打进世锦赛，以二比十不敌格里菲斯<ref>{{cite web | title = Danny Fowler player profile | url = https://www.snookerdatabase.co.uk/PlayerDetails.aspx?PlayerKey=126&tourns=WC&plStat=2 | website = Snooker Database | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2020-09-04 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200904161851/https://www.snookerdatabase.co.uk/PlayerDetails.aspx?PlayerKey=126&tourns=WC&plStat=2}}</ref>。六获世锦赛冠军的[[雷·里尔顿|雷·里尔顿]]以八比十败给[[约翰·坎贝尔_(台球选手)|约翰·坎贝尔]]（{{lang|en|John Campbell}}）<ref name="TIMES13M">{{Cite news | issn = 0140-0460 | title = Sport in Brief: World rise | newspaper = The Times | location = London | date = 1986-05-13 | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F90ADFEDA08E2E1 | access-date = 2020-05-09 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220625/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F0F90ADFEDA08E2E1 }}{{Subscription required}}</ref><ref name="FRISKIN24A">{{Cite news | issn = 0140-0460 | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = Snooker: Francisco forced to work harder | newspaper = The Times | location = London | date = 1986-04-24 | page = 40 | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F90AD188EA88E6B | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220554/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F0F90AD188EA88E6B }}{{Subscription required}}</ref>。

[[道格·芒特乔伊|道格·芒特乔伊]]（{{lang|en|Doug Mountjoy}}）以十比三淘汰[[佩里·芒斯|佩里·芒斯]]（{{lang|en|Perrie Mans}}）<ref name="TIMES21A" />，资格赛晋级选手[[約翰·帕洛特|約翰·帕洛特]]以十比四战胜[[托尼·米奥|托尼·米奥]]（{{lang|en|Tony Meo}}）<ref name="FRISKIN22A" />。[[柯克·史蒂文斯|柯克·史蒂文斯]]（{{lang|en|Kirk Stevens}}）以十比六击败[[迪恩·雷诺兹|迪恩·雷诺兹]]（{{lang|en|Dean Reynolds}}）<ref name="FRISKIN23A" />，[[西尔维诺·弗朗西斯科|西尔维诺·弗朗西斯科]]（{{lang|en|Silvino Francisco}}）以十比四打败[[雷克斯·威廉士|雷克斯·威廉士]]，[[尤金·休斯|尤金·休斯]]（{{lang|en|Eugene Hughes}}）以十比七淘汰[[大卫·泰勒|大卫·泰勒]]（{{lang|en|David Taylor}}），[[埃迪·查尔顿|埃迪·查尔顿]]（{{lang|en|Eddie Charlton}}）以十比六压倒[[克里夫·威尔逊|克里夫·威尔逊]]（{{lang|en|Cliff Wilson}}）<ref name="FRISKIN24A" />。

=== 第二轮 ===
第二轮在4月24至28日举行，采用25局13胜制并分三阶段<ref name="FRISKIN25A" /><ref name="FRISKIN30A">{{Cite news | issn = 0140-0460 | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = Snooker: Davis break clears the way | newspaper = The Times | location = London | page = 32 | date = 1986-04-30 | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F90AD87EB987C87 | access-date = 2020-05-09 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220555/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F0F90AD87EB987C87 }}</ref>。史蒂夫·戴维斯与芒特乔伊首阶段结束时打成四平<ref name="FRISKIN25A" />，第二阶段结束时戴维斯以11比5领先，第三阶段芒特乔伊还没进过球就被对手以13比5淘汰<ref name="EVERTON27A">{{Cite news | last = Everton | first = Clive | title = Snooker: Davis finds champion form | newspaper = The Sunday Times | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F925853AA491FEE | location = London | date = 1986-04-27 | access-date = 2020-05-08 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220554/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F0F925853AA491FEE }}{{Subscription required}}</ref>。希金斯本能以六比二的比分结束首阶段，但他在最后一局击黑球失误，格里菲斯抓住机会扳回一局，双方打成五比三<ref name="TIMES28A" />。格里菲斯第二阶段表现更好，打出单杆110分并追到六平。接下来两人各拿下一局，第15局格里菲斯撞入运气球，第二阶段结束时以九比七领先。<ref name="EVERTON27A" />双方你追我赶一直打到决战局，最后格里菲斯以13比12晋级<ref name="TIMES28A">{{Cite news | issn = 0140-0460 | title = Snooker: Griffiths shatters Higgins's dream | newspaper = The Times | location = London | date = 1986-04-28 | page = 32 | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F90AD5DEF056307 | access-date = 2020-05-09 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220556/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F0F90AD5DEF056307 }}</ref>。史蒂文斯与查尔顿同样打到决战局，史蒂文斯在10比12落后时连追三局以13比12反败为胜<ref name="FRISKIN 29A">{{Cite news | issn = 0140-0460 | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = Snooker: Charlton looks to a Grand Prix | newspaper = The Times | location = London | date = 1986-04-29 | page = 38 | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F90AD7D0EFC8F87 | access-date = 2020-05-09 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220554/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F0F90AD7D0EFC8F87 }}</ref>。

约翰逊首阶段结束时以五比三领先哈雷特，然后以13比6晋级，第13局还打出单杆110分<ref name="FRISKIN26A">{{Cite news | issn = 0140-0460 | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = Snooker: Johnson makes a big advance in his career | newspaper = The Times | location = London | date = 1986-04-26 | page = 40 | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F90AD32B8B55647 | access-date = 2020-05-08 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220555/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F0F90AD32B8B55647 }}</ref>。帕洛特和怀特先后打成四平和六平，怀特随后连下四城，第二阶段结束时以十比六领先<ref name="FRISKIN26A" />。第三阶段开始后怀特在前五局拿下三局，以13比8胜出<ref name="EVERTON27A" />。索恩以13比9战胜[[1985年澳大利亚斯诺克职业锦标赛|澳大利亚职业锦标赛]]冠军坎贝尔<ref name="FRISKIN 29A" />，诺尔斯以13比10打败弗朗西斯科进入八强，索本以13比6淘汰休斯<ref name="FRISKIN30A" />。

=== 八强 ===
4月29至30日举办的八强赛同样采用25局13胜制并分三阶段<ref name="FRISKIN30A" /><ref name="FRISKIN1M">{{Cite news | issn = 0140-0460 | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = Snooker: Dramatic victory for Johnson | newspaper = The Times | location = London | page = 38 | date = 1986-05-01 | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F90ADA9078AD7B3 | access-date = 2020-05-07 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220620/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F0F90ADA9078AD7B3 }}</ref>。约翰逊在第一天比赛结束时以九比七领先格里菲斯，第二天格里菲斯连赢五局以12比9拿到赛点，但约翰逊连下四城以13比12反败为胜，还打出两次单杆破百分<ref name="FRISKIN1M" /><ref name="EVERTON4M">{{Cite news | last = Everton | first = Clive | title = Snooker: Inspired Johnson into final | newspaper = The Sunday Times | location = London | date = 1986-05-04 | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F9258510F0CA915 | access-date = 2020-05-07 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220558/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F0F9258510F0CA915 }}</ref>。史蒂夫·戴维斯与怀特继[[1984年世界斯诺克锦标赛|1984年世界斯诺克锦标赛]]决赛后再度交手，戴维斯第一局就打出单杆134分，随后一直表现出色，以13比5进入四强，怀特比赛期间多次失误<ref name="FRISKIN30A" /><ref name="FRISKIN1M" />。

索本以13比6打败索恩，《[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]》的报道称索恩比赛期间一直没机会流畅发挥<ref name="FRISKIN1M" />。索本以九比三领先后以11比5结束第二阶段，比赛期间夫人芭芭拉在故国加拿大生下他们第二个孩子<ref>{{cite news | title = Thorburn on top of the world! | newspaper = Sandwell Evening Mail | date = 1986-04-30 | page = 35 | via = [[英國報紙檔案館|British Newspaper Archive]]}}</ref>。诺尔斯与史蒂文斯首阶段打成四平，第二阶段打成八平，第三阶段诺尔斯发力，前六局拿下五局，以13比9晋级<ref name="FRISKIN1M" />。

=== 四强 ===
[[File:Steve_Davis_PHC_2012-1.jpg|thumb]]以16比12战胜[[克里夫·索本|克里夫·索本]]第五次打入世锦赛决赛]]

半决赛5月1至3日举行，采31局16胜制并分四阶段<ref name="EVERTON4M" /><ref name="FRISKIN2M">{{Cite news | issn = 0140-0460 | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = Snooker: Pink puts referee on the spot | newspaper = The Times | location = London | date = 1986-05-02 | page = 32 | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F90ADB3F463ACB2 | access-date = 2020-05-07 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220558/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F0F90ADB3F463ACB2 }}</ref><ref name="FRISKIN3M">{{Cite news | issn = 0140-0460 | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = Fortune suddenly deserts Knowles | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_financial-times_1986-05-05_74_46/page/40 | newspaper = The Times | location = London | date = 1986-05-03 | page = 40}}</ref>。约翰逊在首阶段结束时以四比三领先诺尔斯，其中第六和第七局诺尔斯都是因击球入中袋失手落败<ref name="FRISKIN2M" /><ref>{{cite news | title = Knowles mistakes let in Johnson | newspaper = Irish Independent | location = Dublin | page = 13 | date = 1986-05-02 | via = British Newspaper Archive}}</ref>。《泰晤士报》刊登悉尼·弗里斯金（{{lang|en|Sydney Friskin}}）的报道，称约翰逊表现游刃有余，第二阶段结束时把优势拉大到十比五，第三阶段结束时以14比8领先<ref name="FRISKIN3M" />，再在第四阶段开始后连下两城首度打进世锦赛决赛<ref name="TIMES5M">{{Cite news | issn = 0140-0460 | title = Snooker: Davis goes into the unknown | newspaper = The Times | location = London | date = 1986-05-05 | page = 32 | access-date = 2020-05-07 | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/0F90ADC39A3DB563 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220559/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F0F90ADC39A3DB563 }}</ref>。约翰逊因背部[[囊腫|囊腫]]疼痛难忍，服用止痛药后前来参赛，所幸发挥良好<ref name="ROSS2M">{{Cite news | issn = 0319-0781 | pages = 2 | last = Special to The Star | first = Alasdair Ross | title = Thorburn has a bad night against top snooker player | work = The Toronto Star | location = Ontario | date = 1986-05-02 | url = https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/document-view?p=AWNB&docref=news/10B99363F7A57BC0 | access-date = 2020-05-07 | archive-date = 2020-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200905220623/https://infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/news/user/login?destination=document-view%3Fp%3DAWNB%26docref%3Dnews%2F10B99363F7A57BC0 }}</ref>。

史蒂夫·戴维斯在另一场半决赛先以三比二领先索本，第六局索本有望冲击满杆，但在第九个黑球失手，双方打成三平<ref name="ROSS2M" />。戴维斯接下来连下三局，第一天比赛结束时以八比七领先<ref name="FRISKIN3M" />。第三阶段开始后索本以九比八反超，随后又打成十比九，第20局戴维斯打出他在本届世锦赛第五个单杆破百分，双方打成十平。第21局戴维斯打黑球失手，索本再度领先，但马上又被追平。<ref name="EVERTON4M" />接下来六局索本只赢一局，第28局戴维斯打出单杆122分，以16比12第五次进入世锦赛决赛<ref name="TIMES5M" />。

=== 决赛 ===
史蒂夫·戴维斯与约翰逊的决赛在5月4至5日举行，采用35局18胜制并分四阶段，两人此前还从未在职业赛交手<ref name="TIMES5M" /><ref name="FRISKIN6M">{{Cite news | issn = 0140-0460 | last = Friskin | first = Sydney | title = Snooker: Johnson defies odds to win | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_financial-times_1986-05-05_74_46/page/40 | newspaper = The Times | location = London | date = 1986-05-06 | page = 40}}</ref>。外界普遍认为戴维斯会取胜，庄家对戴维斯的赔率是九赔二，对约翰逊是一赔五。戴维斯在首阶段前半截以三比一领先，还打出108和107两次单杆破百分。<ref name="WilliamsGadsby2005">{{cite book | first1 = Luke | last1 = Williams | first2 = Paul | last2 = Gadsby | title = Masters of the Baize: Cue Legends, Bad Boys and Forgotten Men in Search of Snooker's Ultimate Prize | pages = 136–141 | year = 2005 | publisher = Mainstream Publishing | location = Edinburgh | isbn = 978-1-84018-872-1 | chapter = 13. Joe Johnson: Ordinary Joe}}</ref>约翰逊接下来连扳三局，首阶段结束时以四比三反超。戴维斯第二阶段开始后连赢四局，但中场休息后约翰逊又追回四局<ref name="BBC 1986" />，戴维斯拿下第16局打成八平，结束第一天的比赛<ref name="METCALFESL">{{cite web | url = https://www.sportinglife.com/snooker/news/joe-johnson-the-biggest-shock/179206 | title = World Snooker Championship memories: Joe Johnson shocks Steve Davis in 1986 | last = Metcalfe | first = Nick | date = 2020-07-21 | website = Sporting Life | location = UK | publisher = Hestview | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201009130516/https://www.sportinglife.com/snooker/news/joe-johnson-the-biggest-shock/179206 | archive-date = 2020-10-09 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

约翰逊第二天穿上罕见的红、粉、白色皮鞋<ref name="WilliamsGadsby2005" />，比赛开始后他连下四城以12比8领先，其中第18局还有红球入袋的运气球<ref name="METCALFESL" />。第三阶段结束时，约翰逊以13比11领先<ref name="BBC 1986" />。最后一阶段开始后，观众纷纷看好本届世锦赛坚持主动进攻策略的约翰逊<ref name="METCALFESL" />，他在前四局拿下三城，中场休息时以16比12领先<ref name="FRISKIN6M" /><ref name="METCALFESL" />，接下来又赢得第29局拿到赛点，最后在第30局以单杆64分奠定胜局<ref name="BBC 1986" /><ref name="FRISKIN6M" /><ref name="METCALFESL" />。赛前约翰逊[[1985/1986赛季斯诺克职业选手世界排名|世界排名第16]]，赛后[[1986/1987赛季斯诺克职业选手世界排名|升至第八]]<ref name="TIMES13M" />。

戴维斯已是连续第二次在决赛失利，他在接受[[大卫·维恩|大卫·维恩]]（{{lang|en|David Vine}}）采访时表示：“大卫，咱们可不能再在这种情况下见面了”；约翰逊随后表示“希望我们还是朋友”<ref name="METCALFESL" />。约翰逊夺冠后人气高涨并走上电视节目《[[沃根访谈录|沃根访谈录]]》（''{{lang|en|Wogan}}''），还与[[奇里夫·李察|奇里夫·李察]]一起在包厢观看[[温布尔登网球锦标赛|温布尔登网球锦标赛]]<ref name="METCALFESL" />。这是约翰逊职业生涯中仅有的排名赛冠军，他后来拿下1987年苏格兰大师赛和1989年诺维奇联盟大奖赛冠军，但两者都不是排名赛<ref name="METCALFESL" />。戴维斯和约翰逊在[[1987年世界斯诺克锦标赛|次年世锦赛]]决赛重聚，戴维斯以18比14胜利<ref>{{cite web | title = 1987 World Championships Results Grid | url = https://www.snookerdatabase.co.uk/EventResultGrid.aspx?EventKey=25 | website = Snooker Database | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160322013856/http://www.snookerdatabase.co.uk/eventresultgrid.aspx?eventkey=25 | archive-date = 2016-03-22 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Snooker Scene" />。约翰逊注重远距离进球的进攻风格对斯诺克运动影响很大，到20世纪90年代已占主导地位<ref name="WilliamsGadsby2005" />。庄家对约翰逊赢得1986年世锦赛的赔率达1赔150，此前七年职业生涯中他还从未赢得任何赛事冠军，甚至没在克鲁西布剧院赢过比赛<ref name="BBC 1986" />。2020年4月22日，[[2020年世界司諾克錦標賽|2020年世界司諾克錦標賽]]因[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|冠状病毒病疫情]]推迟，[[英國廣播公司第二台|英國廣播公司第二台]]播出1986年决赛的精简版<ref>{{cite web | title = World Snooker Championship: Stephen Hendry & Steve Davis relive Crucible classics | archive-date = 2021-02-12 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.bbc.com/sport/snooker/52294986 | first1 = Shamoon | last1 = Hafez | first2 = Owen | last2 = Phillips | date = 2020-04-17 | work = BBC Sport | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210212231850/https://www.bbc.com/sport/snooker/52294986}}</ref>。

